fields.name: Actions
fields.description: The list of actions that trigger the webhook to post notifications.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the webhook at the time the operation was called.

fields.name: Scope
fields.description: The scope of repositories where the event can be triggered. For example, 'foo:*' means events for all tags under repository 'foo'. 'foo:bar' means events for 'foo:bar' only. 'foo' is equivalent to 'foo:latest'. Empty means all events.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The status of the webhook at the time the operation was called.
